[SHORT DESC]
Immune to Trick and Switcheroo.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>The holder is immune to Trick and Switcheroo.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>Pokemon that hate being Tricked into holding a Choice item, such as Blissey, might enjoy holding Like Mail. However, Blissey would rather use a more beneficial item, such as Leftovers, than Like Mail.</p>

<h2>Location</h2>
<p>Route 9. Also sold in various stores throughout Unova.</p>